[22/03/2017 15:56:21] <font color="#ffffff">A Héctor.</font>
[22/03/2017 15:56:23] <font color="#ffffff">-Violeta.</font>
[22/03/2017 15:56:23] <font color="#00ff00">No es correcto, rebote.</font>
[22/03/2017 15:56:26] <font color="#ffffff">¿Hierba Luisa?</font>
[22/03/2017 15:56:26] <font color="#00ff00">No es correcto, rebote.</font>
